ke":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T05:43:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">聽日見</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i6v9Jdp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi6v9Jdp.jpg&h=6cbe719f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cJFtYML.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcJFtYML.jpg&h=a79b44b6&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T05:49:24.000Z","msg":"The FIVE demands of the protest<br />\n<br />\n1. Full withdrawal of the extradition bill <br />\n<br />\n2. A commission of inquiry into alleged police brutality<br />\n<br />\n3. Retracting the classification of protesters as &ldquo;rioters&rdquo; <br />\n<br />\n4. Amnesty for arrested protesters <br />\n<br />\n5. Dual universal suffrage, meaning for both the Legislative Council and<br />\nthe Chief Executive <br />\n<br />\nFIVE DEMANDS,<br />\nNOT ONE LESS.<br />\nLIBERATE HONG KONG,<br />\nREVOLUTION OF OUR TIMES<br />\n<br />\n撇除政府問題，淨係計警隊，再淨係計721 85 811 新屋嶺  CCTV直送 831，已經夠哂理由比示威者做任何野，包括以武制暴 以眼還眼 百倍奉還<br />\n<br />\n重申七一宣言，立即實行雙普選，推翻港共政權<br />\n<br />\n「勇武派」、「和理非」係角色，唔係派系，理念一致，只係手法不同<br />\n<br />\n唔係仇警，但大家一定要清楚知道點解要清算警隊。警暴（濫捕、濫告、不依法規）係暴政一部分，唔全面改革警隊、監警制度，只會令目前同將來爭取雙普選更加舉步維艱<br />\n<br />\n#五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n#唔撤就罷<br />\n#罷工罷巿罷買罷課<br />\n#我係香港人<br />\n#我參與全港四罷<br />\n#各區集會<br />\n#出核彈麻包袋都唔割蓆<br />\n#直至政府跪低<br />\n#重組警隊 刑事追究 改革監警制度<br />\n#永遠不光顧荃灣北角元朗商戶<br />\n#抵制一切紅媒相關商業活動<br />\n#抵制一切鐵路沿線所有商戶"},{"pid":"e05c66f96d258005364a6b44c0c076f1104fcf48","tid":1567472,"uid":93311,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T05:50:04.000Z","msg":"連港共都開聲讚賞<br />\n真係做得好好啊各位<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/good.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/good.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/good.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c66cf7320756b8b41e4423639fb78c55a008d580","tid":1567472,"uid":7738,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T05:52:10.000Z","msg":"唱歌唔係問題<br />\n做好主線任務 再做支線<br />\n或者唱完歌再貼文宣"},{"pid":"668962c6be88bee42d079cf9aa006a58c870bc46","tid":1567472,"uid":108502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T05:53:21.000Z","msg":"到底呢類post可以loop幾多次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇諗過班和理非如果唔係唱歌嘅話會直接唔出嚟<br />\n準備好星期日啦"}]}